 peel on the apples adds colour to the dessert.<br>- Garnish with fresh mint leaves.<br>- Serve with a scoop of vanilla ice cream.<br>- When entertaining guests, you can make the recipe up to <b>step 4<b> ahead of time. Continue making the sabayon from <b>step 5<b> just before serving the dessert.","Replace cider with apple juice or sparkling wine or Champagne."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","40m","4 portions"]}